{"article_id":"bzAlSNHROr6nAJ95","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"5 Questions For Sessions At The Senate Intelligence Committee Hearing","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The nation 's top legal officer is set to go before Congress on Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to try to defuse a bomb","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that the former FBI director dropped into his lap .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions is scheduled to appear before the Senate Intelligence Committee","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"less than one week after James Comey told the committee","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"he could not discuss openly certain information about Sessions ' recusal from the investigation into Russia 's election meddling last year .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Comey also told the committee","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that Sessions had agreed to clear the Oval Office along with other top administration leaders ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"after which Trump asked Comey to lay off the investigation into former national security adviser Mike Flynn .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Senators want to get Sessions ' take on all this .","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"His strategy :","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Bring it on .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"`` The attorney general has requested","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that this hearing be public , ''","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"said spokeswoman Sarah Isgur Flores .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"`` He believes","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"it is important for the American people to hear the truth directly from him","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and looks forward to answering the committee 's questions tomorrow . ''","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Here 's a look at five questions","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that members likely want to ask Sessions","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"as he both defends himself","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and potentially helps his boss","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"- the president -","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"try to preserve some headway in political seas","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that continue roiling in the aftermath of Hurricane Comey .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The attorney general said early on","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that as someone","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"who had been a campaign partner and advocate for the president ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"he felt","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"it was n't appropriate for him to be in charge of any inquiry into how it had been conducted .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"`` I should not be involved in investigating a campaign","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"I had a role in , ''","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Sessions said at the Justice Department on the day","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"he announced his decision .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"But there are also questions about meetings","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that Sessions had with Russia 's ambassador to the U.S. , Sergey Kislyak ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"who has emerged as a key figure in the question","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"of whether any Trump associates had ties to Russian officials .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Sessions and Kislyak met at least twice last year .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Sessions has denied","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that any of his contact with Kislyak involved discussions about the Trump campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and he has explained","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that as a member of the Senate ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"as he then was ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"he dealt often with foreign emissaries as part of his normal work .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Comey 's hints to the Senate Intelligence Committee , however , suggest","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that he knew of more contacts or other relationships","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"that made him and the rest of the top FBI leaders expect","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"that Sessions would take himself out of the game .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"Whatever they are ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"they 're `` facts","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"that I ca n't discuss in an open setting , ''","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"Comey said .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"`` I have decided to recuse myself from any existing or future investigations of any matters","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"related in any way to the campaigns for President of the United States , ''","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Sessions said in a statement on March 2 .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"`` I have taken no actions","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"regarding any such matters ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"to the extent","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"they exist . ''","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"And yet Sessions took a huge action on May 9 :","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"He signed a letter , with Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"recommending","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"that Trump fire Comey as FBI director .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Trump cited the Justice Department leaders ' recommendation in his now-famous note to Comey","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"concluding","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"that `` you are not able to effectively lead '' the FBI .","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"What 's more , Trump reportedly tasked Sessions with coming up with the case","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"for firing Comey .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"How could an attorney general","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"who said","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"he would take himself out of the Russia investigation","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"play a role","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"in firing the officer","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"who was leading it ?","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"And","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"if Sessions was involved with that decision ,","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"in what other ways might he have continued to be involved with the Russia inquiry","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"even after announcing","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"that he would n't take part ?","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"3 . Did Sessions know","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"what Trump planned to ask Comey in the closed meeting ?","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Comey painted a clear picture for the Senate Intelligence Committee :","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"At the conclusion of a meeting with several people in the Oval Office , Trump","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"- in Comey 's telling -","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"cleared the room .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"`` As the participants started to leave the Oval Office ,","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"the attorney general lingered by my chair","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"but the president thanked him","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"and said","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"he wanted to speak only with me , ''","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"Comey wrote in his statement .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"`` The last person","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"to leave","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"was Jared Kushner","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"[ Trump 's son-in-law and close adviser ] ,","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"who also stood by my chair","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"and exchanged pleasantries with me .","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"The president then excused him ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"he wanted to speak with me . ''","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"That 's when ,","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"in Comey 's telling ,","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"Trump made the ask about the inquiry into the former national security adviser :","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"`` I hope","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"you can let this go . ''","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Did Sessions know beforehand","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"that the president planned to take aside the FBI director","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"and appeal to him to lay off Flynn ?","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"If so ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"had the president asked him beforehand in some other time or place ?","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"if not ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"why did Sessions agree to leave the president alone with someone","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"who was technically his subordinate","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"- the FBI is part of the Justice Department -","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"for a discussion","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"that would have been within his purview ?","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"Sessions ' answers about this and another encounter","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"that Comey has described","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"( more on that below )","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"could be some of the most significant of the hearing on Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"If he confirms","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"there was a meeting","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"at which he and Kushner were asked to leave ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"it could bolster Comey 's account .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"if he challenges this story strongly ,","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"it helps Trump 's narrative","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"that Comey did n't tell the Senate the truth .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"If there is no independent account","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"of what might have taken place inside the White House","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"- in the form of a recording system","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"that might have kept `` tapes '' of the discussions","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"that took place ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"as Trump once suggested on Twitter -","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"it boils down to Trump 's and Sessions ' word against Comey 's .","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"Trump told reporters Friday","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"he 'd have something","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"to say about the tapes `` soon , ''","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"but White House officials have n't given a solid answer","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"about whether they exist -","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"though members of Congress have called for them as evidence","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"if they do .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"White House spokesman Sean Spicer did n't address questions about potential recordings on Monday .","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"4 . Did Sessions ever talk to Trump about the private meeting with Comey ?","depth":6},{"id":147,"text":"Comey told members of Congress","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"that he appealed to Sessions after Trump 's private request :","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"Do n't let that happen again .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"Do n't leave us alone like that .","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"You , the attorney general , have to be between the president and me .","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"California Sen. Kamala Harris asked Comey for more detail about this scene","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"when he appeared last week .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"What did Sessions say ,","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"she asked -","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"how did he respond ?","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"`` I do n't remember real clearly , ''","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"Comey answered .","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"`` I have a recollection of him just kind of looking at me","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"- and there 's a danger here","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"I 'm projecting onto him ,","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"so this may be a faulty memory -","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"but I kind of got","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that his body language gave me the sense , like , 'What am I going to do ? ' ``","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"The Justice Department responded to this in an official statement on the day of Comey 's testimony :","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"`` The attorney general was not silent ;","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"he responded to this comment","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"by saying","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"that the FBI and Department of Justice needed to be careful about following appropriate policies regarding contacts with the White House . ''","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"On Tuesday , Sessions will have the chance to give his own answer in person","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"- or explain to senators what other conversations he and Trump may have had on this subject","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"about which Comey might not have been aware .","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"Members of Congress would love it","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"if their witnesses gave the truth , the whole truth and nothing but the truth -","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"but that is seldom how it actually works .","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"On Wednesday last week , the heads of the top intelligence agencies and the deputy attorney general declined to answer key questions for various reasons .","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"On Thursday , Comey said","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"there were some things","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"he could n't discuss","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"because they involved classified information .","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"And on Tuesday , odds are good that Sessions may also not respond to some of the most pressing questions at the hearing .","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"Top administration officials sometimes argue","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"they should n't disclose the details of what they discuss with the president .","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"Sometimes they tell members of Congress","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"that an answer would divulge classified material .","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"Sometimes they just do n't want to respond ,","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"irrespective of a justification","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"for not doing do .","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"Sen. Angus King , I-Maine , thundered at two top spy bosses last week","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"when they could n't give the legal reasons","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"for why they could n't explain what he wanted .","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"`` I 'm not satisfied with ' I do not believe","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"it is appropriate '","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"or ' I do not feel","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"I should answer , ' ``","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"King said .","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"`` You swore an oath . ''","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"Depending on the extent of what Sessions is willing to discuss on Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"he and King could have a similar exchange .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":399,"left":0,"right":398,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":398,"left":217,"right":397,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":208,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":202,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":1,"right":201,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":204,"right":206,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":4,"right":203,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":7,"right":205,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":216,"left":10,"right":215,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":215,"left":209,"right":214,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":214,"left":211,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":210,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":213,"left":212,"right":18,"relation":"join